name=&quot;XE_cots_package_screening_criteria_and_rationale__artifact_definition&quot;>&lt;/a>&lt;a id=&quot;Purpose&quot; name=&quot;Purpose&quot;>&lt;/a> &#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The purpose of the COTS&amp;nbsp;Package Screening Criteria and Rationale is to record the analytical hierarchy of&#xD;
    measurable criteria used in evaluating the alternative solutions to the stakeholder's business and system requirements.&#xD;
    It provides a single set of selection criteria for COTS packages and vendors to provide the functions and capabilities&#xD;
    required by the stakeholders.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The COTS&amp;nbsp;Package Screening Criteria and Rationale accumulates and organizes information sufficient to:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>Document&lt;/font> &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>preliminary expectations regarding vendor, functional,&#xD;
        operational, architectural, market placement, and supplemental characteristics that must be present for a COTS&#xD;
        package to be considered as part of a solution.&lt;/font>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>Document&lt;/font> &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>rationale describing why these expectations are&#xD;
        sufficiently critical to require all candidate COTS package to comply and how they will distinguish between&#xD;
        candidates.&lt;/font>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>Identify&lt;/font> &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>measurable criteria that correspond to preliminary&#xD;
        expectations.&lt;/font>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>Document a data-gathering strategy and any specific processes and techniques required to&#xD;
        determine whether a COTS package meets measurable criteria.&lt;/font>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>Capture&lt;/font>&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;>, in summary form, any tasks that result in a COTS&#xD;
        package being eliminated from further consideration.&lt;/font>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:ArtifactDescription>
